# Customer Segmentation Dashboard

## Objective
Analyze customer behavior and segment customers based on purchasing patterns.

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- Sample Superstore Dataset

## Features
- Customer Segmentation Analysis
- Sales by Customer Segment
- Profit by Customer Segment
- Customer Distribution by Region
- Category Preference Analysis
- Top 10 Customers
- Interactive Filters

## Key Insights
- Consumer segment generated the highest sales.
- Regional customer distribution was analyzed.
- Category preferences were identified.
- Top customers contributed a significant portion of total sales.

## Outcome
Built a customer segmentation dashboard to understand customer behavior and support business decision-making.
